<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        @page { margin: 0; }
        body { 
            font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif; 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 0; 
            background-color: #f0f2f5;
            color: #1a202c;
        }
        .license-container {
            width: 85.6mm; /* ID-1 format width */
            height: 54mm;  /* ID-1 format height */
            margin: 50px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .top-stripe {
            height: 5px;
            background: #ff6b00;
        }
        .header {
            background: #1a365d;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ff6b00;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-weight: 900;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            opacity: 0.8;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 10px;
        }
        .main-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        .photo-area {
            width: 60px;
            height: 75px;
            background: #edf2f7;
            border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;
            text-align: center;
            vertical-align: middle;
            font-size: 8px;
            color: #a0aec0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .user-details {
            padding-left: 12px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .name {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1a365d;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .sub-info {
            font-size: 8px;
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .info-grid {
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .info-item {
            width: 50%;
            padding-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .label {
            font-size: 6px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #718096;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
        }
        .value {
            font-size: 9px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2d3748;
        }
        .qr-code {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 10px;
            right: 10px;
            width: 35px;
            height: 35px;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding: 2px;
        }
        .qr-mock {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #000, #000 1px, #fff 1px, #fff 3px);
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        .watermark {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-30deg);
            font-size: 40px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: rgba(26, 54, 93, 0.03);
            white-space: nowrap;
            z-index: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .logo-small {
            position: absolute;
            top: 8px;
            left: 10px;
            height: 20px;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        .signature-area {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 10px;
            left: 12px;
            width: 100px;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-top: 0.5px solid #a0aec0;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }
        .signature-text {
            font-size: 5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #718096;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="license-container">
        <div class="top-stripe"></div>
        <div class="header">
            {% if logo %}
                <img src="{{ logo }}" class="logo-small" alt="Logo">
            {% endif %}
            <h1>Fédération La Roue Libre</h1>
            <p>Licence Officielle de Compétition BMX</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="watermark">LA ROUE LIBRE</div>

        <div class="content">
            <table class="main-table">
                <tr>
                    <td class="photo-area">
                        {% if avatar %}
                            <img src="{{ avatar }}" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 4px;" alt="Avatar">
                        {% else %}
                            <div style="padding-top: 25px;">PHOTO</div>
                        {% endif %}
                    </td>
                    <td class="user-details">
                        <div class="name">{{ user.firstname }} {{ user.lastname }}</div>
                        <div class="sub-info">Né(e) le {{ user.birthday|date('d/m/Y') }} • {{ licence.nationaly }}</div>
                        
                        <table class="info-grid">
                            <tr>
                                <td class="info-item">
                                    <span class="label">ID Licence</span>
                                    <span class="value">LR-{{ "now"|date('Y') }}-{{ licence.id|format('%05d') }}</span>
                                </td>
                                <td class="info-item">
                                    <span class="label">Catégorie</span>
                                    <span class="value">{{ licence.priceLicence.label }}</span>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="info-item">
                                    <span class="label">Émis le</span>
                                    <span class="value">{{ "now"|date('d/m/Y') }}</span>
                                </td>
                                <td class="info-item">
                                    <span class="label">Validité</span>
                                    <span class="value">31/12/{{ "now"|date('Y') }}</span>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="signature-area">
            <div class="signature-line"></div>
            <div class="signature-text">Signature du titulaire</div>
        </div>

        <div class="qr-code">
            <div class="qr-mock"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Deuxième carte (Verso) pour plus de professionnalisme -->
    <div class="license-container" style="margin-top: 20px; background: #1a365d; color: white; border: none;">
        <div class="content" style="padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
            <div style="font-size: 10px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #ff6b00; text-transform: uppercase;">Informations Importantes</div>
            <div style="font-size: 7px; line-height: 1.4; color: #e2e8f0; text-align: justify;">
                Cette licence est strictement personnelle et doit être présentée sur demande lors des compétitions officielles. 
                Le titulaire s'engage à respecter le règlement de la Fédération La Roue Libre et les règles de sécurité en vigueur. 
                En cas d'urgence, veuillez contacter les services de secours. 
                Cette carte atteste que le titulaire a fourni un certificat médical valide pour la pratique du BMX en compétition.
            </div>
            
            <div style="margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); pt: 10px;">
                <div style="font-size: 8px; font-weight: bold;">www.larouelibre.fr</div>
                <div style="font-size: 6px; opacity: 0.6;">© {{ "now"|date('Y') }} La Roue Libre - Tous droits réservés</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px; background: #ff6b00;"></div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
